  <bodyText><![CDATA[<p><img src="/media/13049819/chalet-arlhof-st-anton-ext.jpg" alt="chalethero" data-udi="umb://media/f4b02c239d914052afc828d3d2c9e2f9" /></p>
<p>Inghams has a terrific range of accommodation with over 400 properties for you to choose from.</p>
<p>Whatever your preference, you can relax in the knowledge that all of our properties are carefully selected and reviewed annually to ensure they meet Inghams’ high standards for service and quality, including our <a data-udi="umb://document/49b9c2d67d104ca3879a39351d601ab0" href="/{localLink:umb://document/49b9c2d67d104ca3879a39351d601ab0}" title="Inghams Choice Accommodation">Inghams' Choice properties</a> - <span>handpicked by our expert teams of passionate skiers.</span></p>
<p>Select the type of accommodation that best suites your ski or snowboard holiday: </p>
<p><strong>Chalets</strong> - catered ski chalets are the ideal option if you are busy, on the go skiers. With our staff on hand for breakfast, afternoon tea and dinner as well as providing insider knowledge of where to ski, dine out or enjoy some après.  </p>
<p><strong>Apartments</strong> - these are the perfect option if you enjoy that home away from home feel, with fully equipped kitchens you can cook your favorite meals. Always well designed and often linked to local hotels or spas for use of their facilities if they don't already have their own on site. </p>
<p><strong>Hotels</strong> - ideal when you want to kick of your boots and relax at the end of day by enjoying local on-site dining, the use of a pool or perhaps a cosy fire-lit bar. </p>
<p>With all our our accommodation options you can pick from a range of preferences such as ski-in ski-out, luxury, spa or all inclusive. See our <a data-udi="umb://document/7dec408f2e7c459ab8c303a08bc1c68d" href="/{localLink:umb://document/7dec408f2e7c459ab8c303a08bc1c68d}" title="Ski Holiday Types">Holiday Types</a> for more options. </p>
<p><em>See what's new for Inghams ski holidays on our<span> </span><a data-udi="umb://document/4323a332132044fba8041dc874c3bc85" href="/ski-holidays/whats-new-on-the-slopes" title="What's new on the slopes">What's new on the slopes</a><span> </span>page for all the latest on new resorts, offers, accommodation and more.</em><span> </span></p>]]></bodyText>
